        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Ensuring Regulations are Successful or Ended Act of 2017 or the ERASE Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill terminates a federal rule one year after it is finalized unless Congress enacts a joint resolution that provides for the continuance of the rule, or the rule is finalized before the enactment of this bill.</p>]]></text>
